A cyberpunk scene showing a sleek robotic hand hovering over two glowing holographic blueprint panels floating in mid-air, one panel shimmering in electric blue and the other in neon green. The hand's fingers are poised to select between them, with subtle digital particles streaming between the panels suggesting they can be swapped. The background features a dark industrial workspace with exposed circuit-like patterns on the walls emitting soft purple ambient light. Rain streaks across a nearby window, reflecting the holographic glow. The composition emphasizes the moment of choice between two distinct but equally valid paths, with sharp geometric lines and a moody atmosphere of technological precision and control.
